ah-israeli-far-right-minister-says/00000190-687d-d747-add0-e8fd070e0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管威胁不断升级，伊朗并不急于与以色列发生直接冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-escalating-threats-iran-isnt-rushing-toward-a-direct-clash-with-israel/00000190-67f1-d499-a5bf-effffb170000</link><description>随着加沙战争的继续，伊朗继续进行心理战，威胁以色列和拜登政府不要对黎巴嫩真主党发动全面军事行动。但它没有宣布将直接参与此类活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 08:29:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-escalating-threats-iran-isnt-rushing-toward-a-direct-clash-with-israel/00000190-67f1-d499-a5bf-effffb170000</guid></item><item><title>拜登总统辩论惨败可能会诱使美国在中东的敌人考验他的决心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/bidens-presidential-debate-fiasco-may-tempt-u-s-foes-in-the-mideast-to-test-his-resolve/00000190-6594-d0b3-a7d1-67dc5c3e0000</link><description>除了拜登疲倦的表现在民主党中激起前所未有的动荡外，美国的领导力危机预计还将在世界各地引发二次地震，尤其是在中东</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 05:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/bidens-presidential-debate-fiasco-may-tempt-u-s-foes-in-the-mideast-to-test-his-resolve/00000190-6594-d0b3-a7d1-67dc5c3e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府一致再次任命丹尼·达农为以色列下一任驻联合国特使</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-expected-to-re-appoint-danny-dannon-as-israels-next-envoy-to-un/00000190-6525-d747-add0-edfd99610000</link><description>利库德集团成员丹尼·达农将接替过去四年担任以色列驻联合国大使的吉拉德·埃尔丹。这将是达农第二次担任该职位，他于 2015 年至 2020 年间担任该职位</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-expected-to-re-appoint-danny-dannon-as-israels-next-envoy-to-un/00000190-6525-d747-add0-edfd99610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在约旦河西岸发动无人机袭击，袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-live/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-freed-hostages-urge-government-to-reach-deal/00000190-66f3-d90c-a7fc-77f73c5b0000</link><description>自 43 年 10 月 7 日以来，过去 24 小时内，有 37,877 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙被杀。 ■ 以色列国防军：恐怖组织使用加沙市的学校、诊所。 ■ 以色列国防军决定，以色列军队高层现在必须批准在加沙杀害 10 月 7 日恐怖分子。 ■ 斯莫特里奇： “要让真主党退出游戏，一场激烈而迅速的战争是不可避免的”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 02:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-live/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-freed-hostages-urge-government-to-reach-deal/00000190-66f3-d90c-a7fc-77f73c5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布两名士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/two-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-combat-israeli-army-announces/00000190-6580-d499-a5bf-edbec73a0000</link><description>这两名士兵被确认为参谋中士。 Yair Avitan，20 岁，中士。一等（res.）Yakir Shmuel Tatelbaum，21；据以色列国防军称，另有两名士兵受重伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 22:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/two-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-combat-israeli-army-announces/00000190-6580-d499-a5bf-edbec73a0000</guid></item><item><title>获救人质诺亚·阿加马尼敦促“尽一切可能”释放所有人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/rescued-hostage-noa-argamani-urges-doing-everything-possible-to-release-all-hostages/00000190-657d-d367-abbc-6f7f8a130000</link><description>阿加马尼在六月初从哈马斯囚禁中获救后首次公开讲话中表示，“我们不能忘记仍被哈马斯囚禁的人质，我们必须尽一切可能将他们带回家”</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 21:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/rescued-hostage-noa-argamani-urges-doing-everything-possible-to-release-all-hostages/00000190-657d-d367-abbc-6f7f8a130000</guid></item><item><title>美国向哈马斯提供修改以色列支持的加沙停火提案的机会，希望达成妥协</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-offers-hamas-chance-to-amend-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-backed-by-israel/00000190-6523-d499-a5bf-edbfde3b0000</link><description>消息人士称，加沙停火谈判尚未取得任何突破，而哈马斯宣布其政治领导人已与埃及情报部门负责人会面讨论谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 18:36:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-offers-hamas-chance-to-amend-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-backed-by-israel/00000190-6523-d499-a5bf-edbfde3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 267 天：以色列国防军称真主党无人机在以色列西加利利地区爆炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-267-idf-says-hezbollah-drones-exploded-in-israels-western-galilee/00000190-64ca-d367-abbc-6fca28640000</link><description>以色列国防部长：“我们并不是在寻求战争，但我们已经做好了战争准备” ■ 无人机、导弹在以色列加利利地区引发火灾 ■ 美国提出停火/人质释放协议的“新措辞” ■ 伊朗的联合国使命警告称，如果以色列对黎巴嫩“发动全面军事侵略”，“毁灭性战争将会接踵而至” ■ 战争进入 267 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 17:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-267-idf-says-hezbollah-drones-exploded-in-israels-western-galilee/00000190-64ca-d367-abbc-6fca28640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人集会反对内塔尼亚胡联盟，要求加沙停战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/continuing-the-war-means-israel-will-murder-hostages-families-demand-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-6488-d9ec-a19e-e79d4e520000</link><description>一名人质亲属表示，“我们和亲人之间的障碍是内塔尼亚胡坚持不把结束战争作为协议的一部分”。 ■ 警察在特拉维夫抗议活动中强行推搡反对派议员纳马·拉齐米。恳求政府确保加沙所有剩余人质获释</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 15:59:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/continuing-the-war-means-israel-will-murder-hostages-families-demand-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-6488-d9ec-a19e-e79d4e520000</guid></item><item><title>守卫以色列驻塞尔维亚大使馆的警察中箭受伤；袭击者被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-29/ty-article/police-officer-guarding-israeli-embassy-in-serbia-wounded-by-arrow-attacker-shot-dead/00000190-63e4-d9ec-a19e-e7f518130000</link><description>守卫以色列驻贝尔格莱德大使馆的警察颈部被箭射中，随后开枪打死袭击者，目前袭击者身份仍在确定中</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 12:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-29/ty-article/police-officer-guarding-israeli-embassy-in-serbia-wounded-by-arrow-attacker-shot-dead/00000190-63e4-d9ec-a19e-e7f518130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院暂时禁止地方议会没收约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的牛群</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/high-court-temporarily-forbids-local-council-from-sezing-palestinians-herds-in-west-bank/00000190-62e8-d90c-a7fc-77ecb3040000</link><description>近几个月来，约旦河谷地区委员会扣押了属于巴勒斯坦人的牛羊群，理由是它们徘徊或阻碍交通。法院命令理事会停止行动，直到有关此事的请愿得到解决</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 08:19:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/high-court-temporarily-forbids-local-council-from-sezing-palestinians-herds-in-west-bank/00000190-62e8-d90c-a7fc-77ecb3040000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派走上以色列街头，因征兵问题与警方发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-take-to-israels-streets-clash-with-police-over-conscription-to-military/00000190-5eb9-d506-ab9a-7efbc1b50000</link><description>正统派抗议者封锁了一条主要高速公路，恳求他们的政治领导人不要在以色列国防军入伍问题上妥协。大多数人都喊着常见的口号，比如“我们会死，不会被征召入伍”，但也有一些人提出了不同的口号。一名男子对警察大喊：“很遗憾他们没有在 10 月 7 日解决掉你”</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 06:15:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-take-to-israels-streets-clash-with-police-over-conscription-to-military/00000190-5eb9-d506-ab9a-7efbc1b50000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙北部丧生；获释人质敦促政府达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article-live/irans-mission-to-un-if-israel-attacks-lebanon-an-obliterating-war-will-ensue/00000190-61e4-d90c-a7fc-77e4c4ba0000</link><description>以色列国防军：两名士兵在加沙北部的战斗中受重伤 ■ 以色列军队称，部队在加沙城的战斗中杀死了“数十名”恐怖分子 ■ 袭击者在打伤守卫以色列驻塞尔维亚大使馆的警察后被击毙 ■ 以色列军队称，向社区发射了三枚反坦克导弹在国家的北部；没有人员伤亡报告 ■ 两枚火箭从以色列南部加沙地带发射；暂无人员伤亡报告</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 03:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article-live/irans-mission-to-un-if-israel-attacks-lebanon-an-obliterating-war-will-ensue/00000190-61e4-d90c-a7fc-77e4c4ba0000</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构报告称，伊朗计划在福尔多安装一半新离心机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/iran-installs-half-of-planned-new-centrifuges-at-fordow-iaea-report-says/00000190-60bf-d499-a5bf-e9bfc5930000</link><description>外交官表示，增加IR-6机器是对国际原子能机构35国理事会6月5日针对伊朗的一项决议的回应，该决议呼吁德黑兰加强与监督机构的合作，并撤销最近禁止检查人员的做法</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 21:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/iran-installs-half-of-planned-new-centrifuges-at-fordow-iaea-report-says/00000190-60bf-d499-a5bf-e9bfc5930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：三架来自黎巴嫩的无人机在加利利西部爆炸，25枚火箭弹向北部发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-three-drones-from-lebanon-explode-in-western-galilee-25-rockets-fired-at-north/00000190-609d-d009-a9f8-6a9fdf010000</link><description>由于拦截尝试失败，真主党的火箭弹和无人机袭击导致以色列北部两匹马死亡，一辆面包车着火。北方议会主席表示：“纳斯鲁拉一次证明了他是主权者”</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 21:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-three-drones-from-lebanon-explode-in-western-galilee-25-rockets-fired-at-north/00000190-609d-d009-a9f8-6a9fdf010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部国防部长加兰特：“我们并不是在寻求战争，但我们已经做好了准备”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-in-northern-israel-not-looking-for-war-but-ready-for-one/00000190-6062-d499-a5bf-e9fef9b80000</link><description>格兰特告诉士兵，“我们正在准备我们的防御和进攻能力”，并“致力于以外交方式替代战争” ■ 美国攻击舰部署在地中海东部作为“威慑”</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 20:38:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-in-northern-israel-not-looking-for-war-but-ready-for-one/00000190-6062-d499-a5bf-e9fef9b80000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 266 天：以色列国防部长表示，以色列并不希望北方发生战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-266-israel-isnt-the-one-who-wants-war-in-north-defense-minister-says/00000190-5fa5-d90c-a7fc-7fa5bad50000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，它在加沙市舒贾亚附近开展了“地上和地下”行动 ■ 以色列高等法院命令该州在一个月内做出回应，请愿书要求成立国家委员会调查 10 月 7 日的事件 ■ 美国转移军事资产距离以色列和黎巴嫩更近，以防需要撤离美国人 ■ 这是战争开始 266 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 16:53:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-266-israel-isnt-the-one-who-wants-war-in-north-defense-minister-says/00000190-5fa5-d90c-a7fc-7fa5bad50000</guid></item></channel></rss>